    public class InterfaceSectionSetPanel
extends InterfacePanel
implements ShapeListener, java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.ItemListener, WindowListener, InterfaceGraphicListener
    Updated version of InterfaceSectionSet that sets a current section set for a given Graphic2D window, and sets current sections for that window.
